Please don't hold a grudge against Master.

51
00:04:21,089 --> 00:04:22,070
After the poison is eliminated,

52
00:04:22,070 --> 00:04:24,330
whether you want to punish or even kill me

53
00:04:24,750 --> 00:04:25,410
is your say.

54
00:04:26,590 --> 00:04:27,870
We people in the martial world

55
00:04:27,870 --> 00:04:30,110
don't have to kneel when a mistake is made.

56
00:04:30,110 --> 00:04:31,590
I came here today to ask you

57
00:04:32,140 --> 00:04:33,310
about how Mo Haoran

58
00:04:33,550 --> 00:04:34,880
was poisoned back then.

59
00:04:37,030 --> 00:04:39,950
Back then, Empress Dowager Xiao wanted to control His Majesty,

60
00:04:39,950 --> 00:04:42,350
so she poisoned him with the Jialan Poison.

61
00:04:42,710 --> 00:04:44,540
Master used the blood deflection method

62
00:04:44,540 --> 00:04:46,890
to deflect the poison onto himself.

63
00:04:47,270 --> 00:04:49,980
You mentioned a secret medicine from His Majesty that day.

64
00:04:49,980 --> 00:04:50,550
Why?

65
00:04:50,710 --> 00:04:52,030
The medicine couldn't work?

66
00:04:52,030 --> 00:04:55,030
It can just slow down the poison's spread to the heart,

67
00:04:55,060 --> 00:04:57,060
in addition to pain relief effects.

68
00:04:57,680 --> 00:05:00,520
Master must have known there was no cure,

69
