96
00:07:13,310 --> 00:07:13,910
I did.

97
00:07:18,200 --> 00:07:18,950
Good.

98
00:07:20,630 --> 00:07:22,470
Maybe one day when she uses them,

99
00:07:23,190 --> 00:07:24,250
she'll think of me.

100
00:07:30,060 --> 00:07:31,660
I'm afraid she'll forget me,

101
00:07:35,520 --> 00:07:38,250
yet I'm also afraid she won't be able to forget me.

102
00:08:08,580 --> 00:08:09,750
What does he mean?

103
00:08:10,520 --> 00:08:12,720
